metadata.name: Meant to Bee Together
metadata.description:
Echinacea symbolizes strength and health, the Bumble Bee symbolizes community, brightness, and personal power along with wealth, good luck, and prosperity.  
What more could you ask for.  
I watched this fuzzy little worker for quite some time as it carefully maneuvered to collect the pollen from the not-so-soft stamens on this echinacea.  
Nature is just amazing, how everything has a place and purpose. No matter what we humans do, nature continues and gets things done.

Canon 6d | Laowa 60mm 2x macro lens | f5.6 | 1/200sec | ISO 400
